    <h1>Urban Informalities: Street Vendors </h1>
    <p>This map focuses on the Chicago Neighborhood of Little Village. It attempts to review what spaces have the most compatible features for street vendors.  The goal is to identify spaces that have higher compatibilities in hopes that pedestrian improvements can be prioritized in these areas.</p>  
